summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City Light Department, accepting guy wire, and anchor easements in King County, Washington over portions of Lot 9, and Lot 10 all in Lincoln Gardens Addition; Tracts 24, 43, 45 and 46, Moore's Five Acre Tracts; Henry A.
